  "text": "The SPMP method uses Lemma 1 to achieve, at each iteration, the orthogonal projection of a given signal on the selected subspace. In other words, SPMP relays on Lemma 1 to produce an alternative implementation of the OMP approach. Given a signal and a dictionary it proceeds as follows [CITATION_1] : Set S = {∅}, f 0 = 0 and r 0 = f . Starting from k = 1, at each iteration k implement the steps below.",
